        <Parent_String>Edo (Japanese period) [300106643], Early Modern Japanese [300106623], Japanese (culture or style) [300018519], East Asian [300018321], Asian [300018279], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
